{"title":"Sonder Dial up cross-country with affordable aluminium XC hardtail mountain bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/15/sonder-dial-up-cross-country-with-affordable-aluminium-xc-hardtail-mountain-bike/","date":1615820970000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Alpkit’s sister brand Sonder have released their first XC bike, the Sonder Dial. This aluminium hardtail slides into a now comprehensive off-road line-up as their most affordable mountain bike to date. Pricing starts at £299 for the frameset, with three complete builds available too. Here’s a quick intro.</p><h3>Sonder Dial XC MTB</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"sonder dial pan shot action xc mtb alloy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-d