ce-bike-aluminium-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101301/sonder-dial-xc-race-bike-aluminium-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\"></a></p><p>The Sonder Dial 29er hardtail MTB gets a 6066 aluminium tube-set with a race-inspired geometry. Sonder say they’ve engineered some vertical compliance into a low profile flattened top tube for comfort on long rides, while keeping it laterally stiff. As such, the frame has boost rear end spacing (12mm x 148mm).</p><figure id=\"attachment_252952\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252952\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"683\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange-297x169.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange-800x455.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101600/sonder-dial-frameset-only-orange-768x437.jpg 768w,htt