475mm in XL.</p><figure id=\"attachment_252953\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252953\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"465\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-297x115.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-800x310.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-120x47.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-768x298.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-696x270.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-1068x414.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-1084x420.jpg 1084w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-297x115.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-800x310.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-120x47.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-768x298.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-696x270.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-1068x414.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15101908/sonder-dial-internal-cable-routing-1084x420.jpg 1084w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252953\">The Dial gets a threaded 73 mm BSA BB shell</figcaption></figure><p>Seat tubes start at 395mm in small, growing to 520mm in XL. Though none of the three complete build options come spec’d with a dropper seat post, those seat tube lengths should permit use of decent length droppers. Cable routing is internal, including a Stealth port for a dropper.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15104439/sonder-dial-frame-chainstays-boost-spacing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/15104439/sonder-dial-frame-chainstays-boost-spacing.jpg\" alt=\"sonder dial boost spacing affirdable alloy xc mtb frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"933\" si